Class InsertHandler

java.lang.Object
  de.topicmapslab.tmql4j.insert.util.InsertHandler

public class InsertHandler
extends java.lang.Object

Utility class to handle the inserts of topic map items. Class handles all operation which will be proceeded during the interpretation of a insert-expression.

Sven Krosse
